<!-- 1. What is HTML? -->

<!-- HTML stands for Hyper Text Markup Language
HTML is the standard markup language for creating Web pages
HTML describes the structure of a Web page
HTML consists of a series of elements
we can display web page contant like paragraph, lists, images, and links, in structured way using HTML. -->


<!-- 2. What are the new features in HTML5? -->

<!-- * Semantic Elements : <header>, <footer>, <nav>, <article>, <section>, and <aside>
    * Form Elements: date, email, url, tel, and number, month, week, search, file, range, <textarea>, <keygen>, <output>
* Audio and Video Support
